description:
HOME FOR RENT! 

This 3/2 home sits on over a quarter of an acre fenced in yard. This home has an updated septic and drain field, new flooring and fresh paint in most rooms. One car garage with ample amount of storage space + attic space.

Dogs allowed but two pet limit. Must be treated for fleas and ticks. ($350 non refundable pet deposit)

This home is zoned for clay county and has a bus stop at the end of the road perfect for your kiddos. Call text or email for application today!

Included in rent is lawn care and pest control services. Tenant pays water and electric and cable/wifi. No smoking inside the home and pets must be treated for fleas and ticks. Plenty of space for on street parking. Washer and dryer not provided must bring your own.
